The '''Ranphyxes''' were a [[Smashball/Legends|smashball]] team from [[Elom (planet)/Legends|Elom]] during the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]]. [[Zegret Wan]] was its captain. Their nemeses were the [[Corellian Dreadnaughts]].

